    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1926-10-18T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1926-10-18T00:00:00-05:00" n="496"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d496">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">817.00/3923: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Secretary of the Conservative Delegation</hi> (<persName
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Meneses</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">and the Secretary of the Liberal Delegation</hi> (<persName>
                        <hi rend="italic">Camorales</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">at the Corinto Conference to the <gloss type="to"
                            >Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>U. S. S. “<hi rend="smallcaps">Denver</hi>”</placeName> [<date
                            ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-content-and-sibling-dates"
                            calendar="gregorian" when="1926-10-18">
                            <hi rend="italic">undated</hi>
                        </date>].<lb/>[Received October 18, 1926—11:30 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>At the inauguration of the peace conferences on board the <hi rend="italic"
                        >Denver</hi> both delegations send Your Excellency their respects and hope
                    that under the friendly offices of the American Government peace will be
                    restored.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <list>
                            <item>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">J. Barcenas Meneses</hi>
                            </item>
                            <item>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Camorales</hi>
                            </item>
                        </list>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
